snippet.textDisplay: Hey Nintendo, I have a cool new idea for Super Mario Odyssey 2. So it starts off from King Koopa's perspective. The Goomboss is beating up King Koopa, and he demands that King Koopa capture Princess Toadstool and bring her to him. Bowser goes out and tries to nab Princess Toadstool, but luckily Mario 'Jumpman' Mario is there to save the day. But here's the deal: Mario has amnesia and he can't remember how he ended up with amnesia (obviously). As he goes to different kingdoms, he starts to uncover his past, and it is revealed that Mario 'Jumpman' Mario actually paid the Goomboss and company with gold coins to abduct Princess Toadstool because Mario 'Jumpman' Mario really wants to be with her. The Goomboss was just trying to save some effort by having King Koopa abduct Princess Toadstool instead. I don't know what should happen next, so you should end the game there so you can sell copies of Super Mario Odyssey 3 where this all gets resolved. Also, you should make this game available on the Sony Playstation because you will make more money that way.
